&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with technical consultants and subject matter experts to deliver mission-critical customer outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the management of project cost, scope, and schedule; track work to ensure timely deliverables&lt;/li&gt;
