&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with clients to prepare enterprise geospatial strategies, including multi-year implementation and migration roadmaps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collect, organize, and present client requirements, objectives, and business workflows—including asset management, field operations, and data management—to develop actionable ArcGIS Enterprise solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze and interpret business and technical problems specific to water utilities, delivering practical, customer-focused solutions&lt;/li&gt;
