&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review, draft, and negotiate cloud, software, and procurement agreements, for both internal use and incorporation into Esri products and services with vendors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review, draft and negotiate statements of work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond to contract work requests promptly and provide quality, customer-focused support to internal/external customers and suppliers&lt;/li&gt;
